name: A MOMENT IN THE WILD, FROZEN IN TIME.

metadata.name: A Lemur's Posed Perfection
metadata.description:
A photograph that captures the grace and elegance of a lemur in a single, posed moment. A true work of art that showcases the beauty of the wild.

Dimension: 4000 x 6000
300 dpi
Focal Length: 200mm
Gear Used: Nikon D3500

Edition: 1/1

About Artist: I am Benshad Mubarak from Kerala, India. A 28 year old self taught passionate Artist, Photographer and Video Maker. Looking for adventures and awesome moments to capture with my Cameras.
